<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
  <h1 style="color: #333;">You're invited to manage <%= @enterprise_group.name %></h1>
  
  <p>Hello,</p>
  
  <p>You have been invited to become the Enterprise Administrator for <strong><%= @enterprise_group.name %></strong>.</p>
  
  <p>As an Enterprise Administrator, you will have access to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Manage organization members and their roles</li>
    <li>View billing and subscription information</li>
    <li>Configure organization settings</li>
    <li>Access enterprise-level features and support</li>
  </ul>
  
  <div style="background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <p><strong>This invitation will expire in 7 days.</strong></p>
    <p>To accept this invitation and set up your account, please click the button below:</p>
  </div>
  
  <p style="text-align: center;">
    <%= link_to "Accept Invitation", @invitation_url, 
        style: "display: inline-block; background-color: #6366f1; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;" %>
  </p>
  
  <p style="text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
    Or copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
    <%= @invitation_url %>
  </p>
  
  <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
  
  <p>Best regards,<br>
  The SaaS Team</p>
</div>